{{Infobox football biography |name = Pontus Dahlberg |fullname = Pontus Jacob Ragne Dahlberg<ref>{{cite web |title=List of Players under Written Contract Registered Between 01/01/2018 and 31/01/2018 |url=https://www.thefa.com/-/media/files/thefaportal/governance-docs/registrations/january-2018.ashx|publisher=The Football Association |format=PDF |page=2 |accessdate=21 April 2018}}</ref> |image = |birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1999|01|21|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Älvängen]], Sweden |height = 1.94 m |position = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]] |currentclub = [[Watford F.C.|Watford]] |clubnumber = 30 |youthyears1 = 2006–2012 |youthclubs1 = Älvängens IK |youthyears2 = 2015–2016 |youthclubs2 = [[IFK Göteborg]] |years1 = 2015–2017 |clubs1 = [[IFK Göteborg]] |caps1 = 29 |goals1 = 0 |years2 = 2018– |clubs2 = [[Watford F.C.|Watford]] |caps2 = 0 |goals2 = 0 |years3 = 2018 |clubs3 = → [[IFK Göteborg]] (loan) |caps3 = 10 |goals3 = 0 |nationalyears1 = 2014–2016 |nationalteam1 = [[Sweden national under-17 football team|Sweden U17]] |nationalcaps1 = 19 |nationalgoals1 = 0 |nationalyears2 = 2016 |nationalteam2 = [[Sweden national under-19 football team|Sweden U19]] |nationalcaps2 = 3 |nationalgoals2 = 0 |nationalyears3 = 2017– |nationalteam3 = [[Sweden national under-21 football team|Sweden U21]] |nationalcaps3 = 7 |nationalgoals3 = 0 |nationalyears4 = 2018– |nationalteam4 = [[Sweden national football team|Sweden]] |nationalcaps4 = 1 |nationalgoals4 = 0 |club-update = 13:50, 3 July 2018 (UTC) |nationalteam-update = 27 March 2018 }}
'''Pontus Jacob Ragne Dahlberg''' (born 21 January 1999) is a Swedish [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Watford F.C.|Watford]], as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]].
==Club career== On 31 January 2018, Dahlberg signed for [[Watford F.C.|Watford]] on a five-and-a-half-year deal for an undisclosed fee. He was loaned back to [[IFK Göteborg]] until the end of the 2017–18 season.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.watfordfc.com/club/official-dahlberg-deal-done|title=Official: Dahlberg Deal Done|publisher=[[Watford F.C.]]|date=31 January 2018|accessdate=14 March 2018}}</ref>
==International== He made his debut for [[Sweden national football team]] on 7 January 2018 in a friendly against [[Estonia national football team|Estonia]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[ESPN]]|url=http://www.espn.com/soccer/match?gameId=502766|title=Sweden v Estonia game report|date=7 January 2018}}</ref> The game was not officially recognized by [[FIFA]].
